5b83e129712bea6c5ed10e6b2","tid":1539124,"uid":298077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T09:01:16.000Z","msg":"可能爆泠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T09:01:33.000Z","msg":"緊急法?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec6dfe15b031da61eae8c0cbae7b7e17691778d9","tid":1539124,"uid":279279,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T09:01:40.000Z","msg":"如果真係要還min pay, 最少都要「撤回」+「獨立調查」+交1-2個問責官員出嚟啦！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89192d74fe0f1d356ce6c53698728d52aab8d524","tid":1539124,"uid":72800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T09:01:49.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港共殺人政權企圖以<strong>錄音、撤回、學季開始</strong><br />\n轉移<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">太子地鐵傷亡、<br />\n六警壓脊椎休克 <span style=\"color: teal;\">至今嚴重昏迷</span>、<br />\n新屋嶺、民主人權法案、<br />\n臥底實彈、武警滲透、<span style=\"color: green;\">清朝債主權問題</span><br />\n</span></strong></span>連串<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>核彈</strong></span><span style=\"color: red;\">事件焦點<br />\n醒呀大家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">政府帶緊風向</span><br />\n背後繼續大清算 入獄 利刑 一年後被失蹤</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">暗黑兵法劇本 出沒注意：\n\n沒收gear 未來兩星期大量武警喬裝示威者 嫁禍衝擊\n內部分化示威者、\n酷刑凌虐威嚇被捕人士、\n邊緣打壓香港 渲染港獨 阻抗爭之風蔓延內陸、\n假新聞、擺拍、編輯、洗腦文宣製造風向 污名化運動、\n暴力鎮壓 拘捕 扣留 私刑 企圖瓦解前線、\n文宣 抹黑 嫁禍 插贜 示威者、\n暗殺 第一滴血 企圖逆轉民意 國際譴責、\n市民絕望噤聲 憤怒冷卻、\n中立派 賺錢派 政治疲勞、\n鼓吹經濟下滑風向 富豪商家屈服 加速瓦解、\n學季始開，拖延 分散 擊破、\n白色恐怖、清除異己、染紅香港\n\n拖字訣 雨傘結局 ⋯</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n袋住先 放風降溫<br />\n大追捕 清算 正式開始<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><sp